text:
The show must go on, small theaters claim in a new lawsuit against Gov. Cuomo’s coronavirus shutdown orders.

Eight theaters, including the Broadway Comedy Club, Actors Temple Theater and SoHo Playhouse, claim regulations are unfairly applied.
https://t.co/ujk8meMycQ

name: NYDailyNews
text:
A grand juror in the Breonna Taylor case, speaking anonymously to CBS News, said the Louisville police officers' behavior in the fatal shooting was “criminal.”

The two cops who shot the Black medical worker saw no charges, infuriating protesters.
https://t.co/hG5ito6ShO

name: NYDailyNews
text:
RT @NYDailyNews: DeOndra Dixon, actor Jamie Foxx’s sister, has died at age 36. 

“My heart is shattered into a million pieces,” Foxx wrote on Instagram.

Dixon was an ambassador for the Global Down Syndrome Foundation since 2011.
https://t.co/jkQpgpSDJf

The body was that of 25-year-old Virginia rapper Brian Trotter.
